## Level 3 Task 2 â€“ File Encryption & Decryption

This project demonstrates file encryption and decryption using Fernet encryption in Python.

### Features
- Encrypts text files
- Decrypts encrypted files
- Uses secure key-based encryption

### Technologies
- Python
- cryptography (Fernet)

### How to Run
1. Install cryptography
2. Run encrypt_decrypt.py
3. Choose E to encrypt or D to decrypt
